OL,4,G0005F999: On the Front Line
OL,5,     GParamedics are called to a man
OL,6,     Gwith chest pains, a woman with
OL,7,     Gliver disease, a patient with one
OL,8,     Gkidney and a boy who's fallen on
OL,9,     Ghis face.
OL,10,G0110F24 Hours in A&E
OL,11,     GNurse Emma has a narrow window of
OL,12,     Gtime to help 71-year-old Thomas
OL,13,     Gafter a suspected stroke. And 97-
OL,14,     Gyear-old Leslie is brought to A&E
OL,15,     Gafter experiencing persistent
OL,16,     Gnosebleeds.
OL,17,G0215F24 Hours in A&E
OL,18,     GPam, who's 82 and has
OL,19,     GAlzheimer's, is brought into St
OL,20,     GGeorge's with suspected sepsis.
OL,21,     GTheo, who's 27, has hurt his knee
OL,22,     Gplaying football.
